snippet.title: Town of Salem 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2140510/Town_of_Salem_2
Town of Salem 2 is releasing into Early Access May 26th, 2023! 

The Town of Salem is in turmoil as the Coven has taken over. Will you have what it takes to survive?

Twitter: https://twitter.com/townofsalemtwo

If you are interested in a press kit, you can find it here: 
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ycbwCwxQB2xUD01VZVr2Fwvi27J6aC6V/view?usp=sharing
